This program can correct the data about the films stored in the dynamic structure,
it is also possible to add and delete films from the list, display all the information about all films,
display the name of films with a duration of more than an hour, and display the name of films released after the year entered.
It is possible to sort by the field of distribution and search for all the films in the given mode, and the program has an interface that
allows you to enter data and get the result, and the program can read the data about the film from the file and also write to the file.
